b
da = R_n
db = R_m
R_n \leq R_m
R_m = R_n\cdot 10^{m-n} + R_{m - n}
d | R_n\cdot 10^{m-n} \implies d|R_{m-n}
R_{m+n} = R_m\cdot 10^n + R_n = db\cdot 10^n + da = d(10^nb + a) \implies d|R_{m+n}
